---
title: Tandoori Chicken Thigh Masala Curry with Spinach, Basmati Rice and Crispy Onions
description: Masala curries are versatile tomato-based dishes that work with a variety of proteins and vegetables. Here, we're using a classic with chicken, perfect for soaking up the delicious flavour of the masala curry sauce.
